com.beepell.repository
Class ServiceRepository

java.lang.Object
  com.beepell.repository.ServiceRepository

public class ServiceRepository
extends Object

A repository for receiving and containing definitions written in the Web Service Definition Language (WSDL). Besides the WSDL standard definitions, such as port type, operation and message, it contains WS-BPEL specific definitions: Property, Property Alias, Partner Link Type and Roles. The WSDL standard definitions are parsed using an implementation of JSR 110: Java APIs for WSDL. Property, Property Alias, Partner Link Type and Roles are implemented separately. Note that, process definitions does not share repositories. Different process definitions may use different versions of definitions in the namespace.

Author:
Tim Hallwyl
